People calls her “Mizuki” or “Mii-chan"
戸北美月 (Japanese Kanji name)
Born December 29 1999
Blood type O
In Fukuoka City, Fukuoka Prefecture, Japan
Capricorn (constellation)
Height: 169 cm

Education: Doshisha University

Pets: Rabbit (name/Watage) 
Hobbies: Sake brewery tour, cooking, piano
Sports: Swimming, Work out, Hit the gym
Special skill: Japanese Sake test second grade
